  <h2>System Requirements</h2>

  <h3>Controller</h3>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Component</th><th>Requirement</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>OS</td><td>Linux (Docker recommended)</td></tr>
      <tr><td>CPU</td><td>2 cores minimum, 4+ recommended</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Memory</td><td>512 MB minimum, 2 GB recommended</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Database</td><td>PostgreSQL 16+</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Ports</td><td>8080 (HTTP/WebSocket), 9443 (gRPC)</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Storage</td><td>10 GB for application and logs; database grows ~50 MB per 10,000 jobs</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h3>Agents</h3>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Component</th><th>Requirement</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>OS</td><td>Windows Server 2019+ / Windows 10+ / Linux (Ubuntu 22.04+)</td></tr>
      <tr><td>GPU</td><td>NVIDIA (NVENC), Intel (QSV), or AMD (AMF) with hardware encoder support</td></tr>
      <tr><td>CPU</td><td>4 cores minimum for software encode; 2 cores sufficient for GPU-only encode</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Memory</td><td>4 GB minimum, 8–16 GB recommended</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Network</td><td>Outbound TCP to Controller port 9443; LAN access to media storage</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Local Storage</td><td>3× the largest expected source file for chunked encoding temp files</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>Technology Stack</h2>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Layer</th><th>Technology</th><th>Purpose</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>Controller backend</td><td>Go 1.25+</td><td>REST API, gRPC server, scheduler, template engine</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Agent backend</td><td>Go 1.25+</td><td>gRPC client, job runner, codec plugin host</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Web frontend</td><td>React 19 + Vite 8 (embedded via embed.FS)</td><td>Dashboard SPA embedded in the Controller binary</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Database</td><td>PostgreSQL 16+ with pgx</td><td>Controller state: jobs, agents, presets, users</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Agent journal</td><td>SQLite</td><td>Offline-resilient local job state on each Agent</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Transport</td><td>gRPC + Protocol Buffers</td><td>Controller-Agent communication over mTLS</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Observability</td><td>Prometheus + OpenTelemetry</td><td>Metrics scraping and distributed tracing</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Dashboards</td><td>Grafana</td><td>Pre-built dashboards for operational monitoring</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Container runtime</td><td>Docker / containerd</td><td>Recommended deployment method for the Controller</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
